sentences: Lanaé (aka Lanae' Hale) (born September 15, 1983) is an American singer and songwriter from Florida.
She has released three works: an EP, Lanae' Hale EP, in 2007, a full-length release, Back & Forth, in 2009 and an EP, Lanaé, in 2017.
